<%
const fullName = getFullName({ firstName: authorFirstname, lastName: authorLastname})
%>

<%= storyLine %>
The main person in the story is <%= person.name %>.
Mention the following facts about <%= person.name %>.
<% if (person.gender !== "n/a") { %>
  The gender of <%= person.name %> is <%= person.gender %>.
<% } %>
The person is born in the year <%= person.birth_year %>

Include <%= fullName %> as author of the story, 
and mention the publication date which is <%= formatDate(new Date()) %>.